---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '@/components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Electricity Load Calculator"
  description="Our privacy policy explains how Electricity Load Calculator handles your data. All calculations run locally in your browser — your appliance data is never sent to our servers."
  keywords="electricity load calculator privacy policy, data privacy, no data collection"
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Privacy Policy' }]} />
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-8 md:pt-12 pb-12 md:pb-16 animate-slide-up">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-text-primary">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-text-muted">Last updated: June 08, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-base leading-relaxed">
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Electricity Load Calculator ("we", "our", "the service") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights. The short version: our core calculator runs locally in your browser, but we use third-party services like Google AdSense which utilize cookies to serve advertisements.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            We do not require you to create an account or provide any personal information to use the Electricity Load Calculator.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            The calculator tool runs entirely in your browser. Any data you enter (such as custom appliances, wattages, or regional settings) is processed locally on your device and is never transmitted to our servers.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            We may collect non-personal, aggregated data through standard server logs and analytics, such as browser type, operating system, and approximate geographic region, to ensure the site functions correctly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">2. Advertising and Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            To keep this tool free, we use third-party advertising companies, including Google AdSense, to serve ads when you visit our website.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites on the Internet.</li>
            <li>Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to you based on your visit to our sites and/or other sites on the Internet.</li>
            <li>You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-text-primary hover:text-accent underline decoration-border underline-offset-4">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            We use external services to deliver our content efficiently. For example, we may use content delivery networks (CDNs) or external fonts. When your browser downloads these assets, the third party may log your IP address as part of standard web delivery.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Our site may contain links to external sites that are not operated by us. Please be aware that we have no control over the content and practices of these sites, and cannot accept responsibility or liability for their respective privacy policies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">4. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Because the calculator processes your input locally, we do not store your calculation data on our servers. Server access logs, if retained for security and analytics, are kept for a limited time and are used solely to diagnose technical issues and analyze site performance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">5. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Electricity Load Calculator is a general-purpose utility tool suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. Since we do not request personal information from any user, this service complies with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) by design.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Because our core application does not collect identifiable personal data, there is typically nothing for us to retrieve, correct, or delete on your behalf. If you have contacted us via email and wish for that correspondence to be deleted, please contact us and we will respond promptly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">7. Changes To This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the service after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4 border-b border-border pb-2">8. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Questions about this Privacy Policy? Please visit our <a href="/contact-us" class="text-text-primary hover:text-accent underline decoration-border underline-offset-4">Contact page</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
